    slug: "what-is-a-kpi-target",
    title: "What Is a KPI Target and How Do You Set One?",
    description: "A KPI target is the performance level you are aiming to hit. Learn how to set targets that are realistic, motivating, and useful.",
    category: "Business Intelligence Basics",
