    slug: "what-is-sell-through-retail",
    title: "What Is Sell-Through Rate in Retail?",
    description: "Sell-through rate measures how much of your inventory has been sold in a period. The key metric for managing stock health and markdown risk.",
    category: "Retail & Physical Commerce",
