    title: "What Is Cost-Plus Pricing?",
    description: "Cost-plus pricing sets your price by adding a fixed margin on top of your costs. Simple to implement, but it has real limitations every SME owner should know.",
    category: "Pricing Strategy",
    categorySlug: "pricing-strategy",
