    slug: "what-is-esg",
    title: "What is ESG?",
    description: "A plain-English introduction to Environmental, Social and Governance criteria — what they mean, why they matter, and how SMEs are increasingly expected to engage with them.",
    category: "Sustainability & ESG",
    categorySlug: "sustainability-and-esg",
