    slug: "pos-business-pulse-impact",
    title: "How POS Transactions Affect Your Business Pulse Score",
    description: "Your Business Pulse score factors in POS revenue trends, inventory health, and transaction patterns. Here is exactly how it works.",
    category: "Point of Sale & Retail",
    categorySlug: "point-of-sale",
